# Public Repositories for Erlware Development

## Official Repositories

These are the repositories with the [official Erlware code][erlware]; their
master's head compose the head of Erlware's development.

If you are going to contribute code to any application, please take a look at
[development model]({relocatable:index.page}) and
[standards]({relocatable:standards.page}) first.

Apart from application repositories, `erlware-site` repository contains the
sources to build [Erlware site;][site] see
[Erlware Site's Documentation]({relocatable:erlware-site.page}) for more
information about this.

